Ametek Inc said its board approved aprogram to purchase the company's stock.    It also announced directors will review increasing thequarterly dividend at their regular November meeting,considering a payment of 15 cts a share on the recently splitstock. Ametek said this would be equal to 30 cts a share on thepresent shares, up from the 25 cts quarterly paid previously.    The company provided no details on its stock repurchaseprogram. It noted such purchases have been made fromtime-to-time in the past. Reuter&#3;